  "design_notes": "S0 (Intro): Quiet build up using light jacks to mark the initial vocal beats. S1-S2 (Builds): Transition into standard step flows drifting from side to side. S3-S5 (First Drops): Intense jumpstream and stream sections hitting the active vocal rhythms and percussion accents. S6 (Transition): Standard steps with lighter crossovers. S7-S9 (Heavy Drop): Maximum energy stream with box movements and holds to capture sustained vocals. S10 (Outro): Safe stops_breather to let the player cool down.",
